follows from `gammaProd_pos` (the tuple has distinct entries, giving at least
one nontrivial gcd). The upper bound follows from each `gammaRow j` dividing
`∏_{i<j} |h'_j − h'_i| ≤ H^j`, so `γ ≤ H^{k(k−1)/2} ≤ H^k` when `k ≤ 3`,
